OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777036267
OL,3,CMan charged with murder following
OL,4,Cdeath of cyclist
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder and
OL,7,Fa number of other offences after the
OL,8,Fdeath of a cyclist.
OL,10,FMichael Mullins was killed in a
OL,11,Fcollision as he cycled in Altrincham
OL,12,Fon the evening of Monday, 20 April.
OL,14,FThe 56-year-old, a father and
OL,15,Fgrandfather, had been headteacher of
OL,16,FStretford Grammar School in Trafford,
OL,17,Ffor 17 years and lived with his family
OL,18,Fin Weaverham, Northwich.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
