FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777036267
OL,3,CMan charged with murder following
OL,4,Cdeath of cyclist
OL,6,FIn a statement issued through Greater
OL,7,FManchester Police (GMP) after his
OL,8,Fdeath, his family said: "Our loving
OL,9,FDad, husband, Brother-in-law, 'Diddy',
OL,10,FUncle, Son in law, passed away last
OL,11,Fnight after being knocked off his bike.
OL,13,F"He was devoted to his family and our
OL,14,Flives will never be the same. A gap
OL,15,Fhas been left in our hearts and within
OL,16,Fhis role as a headteacher of Stretford
OL,17,FGrammar school.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777036267
OL,3,CMan charged with murder following
OL,4,Cdeath of cyclist
OL,6,F"Our Dad gave us fantastic memories
OL,7,Fgrowing up including a trip getting
OL,8,Flost at night around Washington D.C
OL,9,Fbut it was in his role as a Grandad
OL,10,Fwhere he truly excelled.
OL,12,F"At this time the family request
OL,13,Fprivacy. Our love and memories of
OL,14,FMichael will know no limits. We will
OL,15,Flove him forever, to Saturn and
OL,16,Fbeyond."
OL,18,FTributes at school gates as grammar
OL,19,Fschool mourns bicycle death of
OL,20,F'devoted' head teacher
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
