PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777036267
OL,3,CMan charged with murder following
OL,4,Cdeath of cyclist
OL,6,FSimon Richardson, 34, will appear in
OL,7,Fcourt on Friday 24 April, charged with
OL,8,Fmurder, manslaughter, dangerous
OL,9,Fdriving, failing to stop, and driving
OL,10,Fwithout insurance.
OL,12,FGMP said the vehicle involved in the
OL,13,Fcrash failed to stop, but four people,
OL,14,Fthree men and a woman, were later
OL,15,Farrested on suspicion of causing death
OL,16,Fby dangerous driving.
OL,18,FOfficers are appealing for witnesses
OL,19,Fand anyone who may have video footage
OL,20,Fto get in touch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
